          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Auto lenders</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">BNPL providers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Medical lenders</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Dental financing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Subprime / near-prime operators</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">SMB working capital</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Specialty finance</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-light rounded-lg">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-darkest font-medium">Niche lending categories</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-dark mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Whether you're early in scaling or already doing millions per month, PrimeBridge gives you a capital partner without the complexity of traditional credit facilities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What You Get -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-light">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-darkest mb-4">
            Infrastructure that removes friction from private credit
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Automated Tape Validation</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">Clean, structured, investor-ready loan data. We handle the formatting so you don't have to.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Dedicated Deal Room</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">Each pool gets its own deal room. Investors see exactly what they need to evaluate and commit.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Predictable Timelines</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">Faster than banks. More transparent than credit funds. Know where you stand at every step.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Investor Diversification</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">Don't be dependent on one capital source. Access multiple investors through a single platform.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Flexible Deal Structures</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">We standardize the pipe, not your product. All covenants, triggers, and enhancements remain yours.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkest mb-3">Full Transparency</h3>
            <p class="text-dark leading-relaxed">Real-time visibility into investor interest and commitment levels throughout the process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why PrimeBridge Works -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-darkest text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
            We're not a marketplace. We're infrastructure.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            Other platforms fail because they try to standardize the credit product. That's impossible. Every lender has different underwriting, covenants, triggers, credit enhancements, and risk models.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10">
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
              PrimeBridge standardizes the <span class="text-primary-light">workflow</span>, not the loan.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Think <strong class="text-white">Stripe for private credit</strong>: We unify the data layer so bespoke deals can move faster.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Early Lender Program -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-10 border border-primary/20">
            <div class="text-center mb-10">
              <span class="inline-block bg-primary text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Early Lender Program</span>
              <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-darkest mb-4">
                List your first pool and get:
              </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-darkest mb-1">Priority Distribution</h3>
                  <p class="text-dark text-sm">First access to our investor network</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
